---
title: Sheet Pan Monterey Jack Un-Fried Chicken with Roasted Asparagus, Potato Wedges & Sriracha Mayo
description: Craving fried chicken? These cheesy panko-breaded cutlets are so crispy you’ll be surprised they’re baked! We serve ’em with Sriracha-spiked mayo and a side of roasted carrots and equally crispy potato wedges. If this all sounds complicated—it’s not! This delicious dinner can be on the table in just 35 minutes.
